msgstr ""

#: src/Privacy/PrivacyPolicyGenerator.php:60
msgid "Statnive does not use cookies, localStorage, sessionStorage, or any form of browser fingerprinting. Visitor identification uses a daily-rotating cryptographic hash that cannot be reversed or used to track individuals across days."
