#: src/Privacy/PrivacyPolicyGenerator.php:74
msgid "IP Address Handling"
msgstr ""

#: src/Privacy/PrivacyPolicyGenerator.php:75
msgid "Your IP address is never stored. It is used only momentarily to determine your approximate geographic location and to generate a one-way cryptographic hash for visit counting. The IP is discarded immediately after processing and cannot be recovered from the stored hash."
msgstr ""

